# Keep the build context small and reproducible: never ship host artifacts.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.output
**/.vite
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/*.log

.git
.gitignore
.github
.planning
.vscode
.idea
.claude

# Local env files must not leak into images; pass config at build/run time.
**/.env
**/.env.*

**/*.md
Dockerfile*
.dockerignore
